cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image processing using deep learning techniques, specifically deep convolutional neural networks (CNNs). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves image compression and feature extraction, which are related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM). The use of deep learning algorithms also falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE).
